data.description: Welcome to 616 Spruce Street! Take a look at this 3 bedroom remodeled home with so much charm! Move right in and enjoy your attached garage, private deck overlooking a large, private fenced yard with a “ready to grow” fenced raised bed garden. On the inside of the home--lovely hardwood floors throughout, NEW kitchen, renovated bathroom, updated PEX plumbing, updated electrical and newer forced air furnace. Classic layout with main floor bedrooms, upper level is perfect for an office or another bedroom and much untapped potential in the lower level. Ideal location; this adorable home is in walking distance of numerous parks and tennis courts.
